        " لَيْسَ طَلَاقُ الصَّبِيِّ بِشَيْ‏ءٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Muhammad Bin al Fuzayl, from Abu Al Sabbah Al Kinany, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘A divorce of the child is not with anything’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from Muhammad ibn ’Isma‘il from Muhammad ibn al-Fudayl from abu al-Sabbah al-Kinaniy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that divorce of a child does not have any valid effect.’” "
        ]
      }
